data.description: Beautiful Freshly Painted home in with newer luxury vinyl floors on the main level. this 3500 sq ft  3 car garage home has abundance of space with 5 bedroom 3 full baths with a bedroom on the main level. Gourmet kitchen off white maple cabinets with ex-large island with granite counter tops, stainless appliances walk in pantry. Great room with gas fireplace, private built-in office with desk, built in family organizer for coats & back packs.  Upstairs features: large master suite with soaking tub, walk in shower, double vanity,  3 additional bedrooms, oversized loft that offers all kinds of options . Sliding glass doors leading out to Fully fenced backyard, playset & covered patio.
